{"tid":1967551,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"Pioneer Pet 不銹鋼飲水機定係Petkit Eversweet 第三代飲水機好？","createTime":"2020-04-11T04:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T03:23:59.000Z","uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc990c1c8b497a2b555f4a7008568d583d61cfb","tid":1967551,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"本身用緊Petkit 第二代，有污糟嘢入咗水泵入面，洗極都唔乾淨。<br />\n佢個水泵又冇得單獨換，所以想換過部新嘅飲水機。<br />\n<br />\n 暫時睇緊下面呢兩款，有冇人用緊／用過？覺得邊款好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.hktv-img.com/images/HKTV/10883/pkw4a_other_35958687_20200323162831_01_1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.hktv-img.com%2Fimages%2FHKTV%2F10883%2Fpkw4a_other_35958687_20200323162831_01_1200.jpg&h=e62cb40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">b]Petkit - Eversweet 3代不鏽鋼智能飲水機[/b]</span><br />\n-水流接觸面採用304不鏽鋼設計，佔整體通水結構85%<br />\n<br />\n-飲水盤採用嬰兒奶樽Tritan材質，經FDA認證不含BPA<br />\n<br />\n-三重過濾濾芯去除雜質、氯氣及重金屬，軟化水質，達人用級標準，提供潔淨水源<br />\n<br />\n-xSecure生命保障系統，配有後備電池及電池低電量提示，停電自動切換電池模式，可工作至少七天<br />\n<br />\n-Smart模式自動感光日夜變頻,Normal模式持續噴水<br />\n<br />\n-每日四次智能脈沖推浮毛，增壓噴湧，將飲水盤上浮毛推至濾芯，保持潔淨<br />\n<br />\n-內置水位感應器，缺水時自動開啟斷電保護模式，防止水泵乾燒<br />\n<br />\n-上下分離式設計方便清洗及換水，飲水盤螺旋式鎖扣設計防止寵物損壞<br />\n<br />\n-睡眠級靜音系統，二代低壓靜音水泵配合羅馬柱型水流結構，工作噪音低於30分貝，比上一代降低25%<br />\n<br />\n-分離式水泵設計，水泵損壞可獨立更換<br />\n<br />\n-寵物功學高度設計,可舒緩頸椎壓力問題<br />\n<br />\n-更換濾芯提示燈,通過水泵噴水量計算更換週期<br />\n<br />\n-1.5米Usb防咬電源線供電，環保慳電，Smart模式操作平均3個月消耗1度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.petdoghk.com/media/catalog/product/cache/c687aa7517cf01e65c009f6943c2b1e9/p/i/pioneer_pet_60oz_1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.petdoghk.com%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2Fc687aa7517cf01e65c009f6943c2b1e9%2Fp%2Fi%2Fpioneer_pet_60oz_1_.jpg&h=550122dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Pioneer Pet - 水滴型不銹鋼循環寵物飲水機 </strong></span><br />\n・循環流動水源會更吸引寵物飲用<br />\n・可更換的木炭過濾器，令水源更清潔和純淨<br />\n・易於清潔<br />\n・使用不銹鋼碗有助於保護寵物免受細菌感染<br />\n・1.77L容量可以減少您每天需要補充的次數<br />\n・為獲得最佳性能，我們建議您每周清潔飲水機一次，並每月拆卸/清潔一次水泵。<br />\n・適用對象：貓咪或中至小型犬隻<br />\n・尺寸：L280mm x W230mm x H102mm"},{"pid":"0b84a43d88a58e3f1aa3a5c378a22bd5ee319233","tid":1967551,"uid":121984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:04:54.000Z","msg":"最好用碗 定時換"},{"pid":"fbd3387b09d3966eb0509ac761a9ac8248cc3e35","tid":1967551,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b84a43d88a58e3f1aa3a5c378a22bd5ee319233","tid":1967551,"uid":121984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:04:54.000Z","msg":"最好用碗 定時換"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"我隻貓淨係飲活水，放碗佢唔飲"},{"pid":"5ea0f5735232413d15e2b7b7290eef441fb74417","tid":1967551,"uid":120705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"兩個都買晒<br />\n越多出水位<br />\n飲水機會越大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99f8ef2edc75b189761000cfaa32ae75d81c7af","tid":1967551,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:40:29.000Z","msg":"Petkit 好似試過漏電..."},{"pid":"d8a5d69687c3da49b75164dde4b18a3e43ce14a2","tid":1967551,"uid":11581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:15:47.000Z","msg":"Petree 穩陣d <br />\n貓卜力有隻都好似幾好 可以試下"},{"pid":"3b13097fd85fe26e95cd591c628f2ae4b6b94ed3","tid":1967551,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"你有冇拆開個水泵洗先？"},{"pid":"15adc5137682709e06cd67c6ae9c0b816914ba89","tid":1967551,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d99f8ef2edc75b189761000cfaa32ae75d81c7af","tid":1967551,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:40:29.000Z","msg":"Petkit 好似試過漏電..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-